{"tid":2175371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實同「廢青」拍過拖，真係返唔到轉頭","createTime":"2020-08-26T12:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T14:19:57.000Z","uid":157483,"like":25,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"de8526f0d9e51186d507051d7c82b4a59d540e68","tid":2175371,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"之前有一任 係岩岩grad未有野做既 時間比較多<br />\n基本上text係會秒回或者分回，基本上搵親佢佢都係度<br />\n所以佢地會比到你好及時好快速既關心，係出面有咩壓力佢都可以好即時咁comfort到我 幫我分擔，會係一個好好既分擔對象<br />\n而且好易約，約行街食飯命中率都好高，一放假直頭可以日日二人世界，可以做到長期陪伴<br />\n而且因為世藝比較少，佢地既世界入面 另一半係會佔好大比重，所以會好愛你好緊張你 唔會唔爹唔吊<br />\n所以各位另一半如果係呢類人既話，唔好睇唔起佢唔洗逼佢做野，因為未嘗唔係好事"},{"pid":"c043f236b2632dc2fd25064007bf63c94c0c8129","tid":2175371,"uid":143343,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afe1b16091474a4636623d22ccafd471dcdc27a7","tid":2175371,"uid":143343,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4773b23950e69418940957f031f63be392f3f6d","tid":2175371,"uid":9392,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦屌你老母西"},{"pid":"28d4c0fc8f3eed162fb67ea89b21a1c60c301e50","tid":2175371,"uid":157483,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"大家唔洗理上面幾隻比我block左既cc台白卡佬"},{"pid":"ff1b547e4f053bf79d799d06567a2d124195a237","tid":2175371,"uid":286155,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"afe1b16091474a4636623d22ccafd471dcdc27a7","tid":2175371,"uid":143343,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"感謝提醒<br />\n我會提防樓主的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3ca1c2a13ec924d3d97236eb5ed85716b3cf18","tid":2175371,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:24:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ac0d60ce90